This means they go. basicly your nazgul deck is about beating up. with drawn to it&#39;s power and blade tip u can curropt but basicly u make ur opponent worry about it. Anyway agasint popular legolas and aragorn bow decks al blades perish protects ur guy for a key fight while a black breath or blade tip ends one of them.<br />
<br />
Anyway with aragorn and arwen u can heal and arwens fate which is cool. Athelas is to remove conditions. cause wounds aren&#39;t that much of a problem with such a strong fellowship. I think you want to move 2 sites a turn and you will in most cases. except for when your opponent has 2-3 guys left or one huge guy left. at which point stay put. your nazgul will hav the same efect.<br />
<br />
with nazgul always remember that your key idea is to slow opponent down. if u have a guy get him out over a condition. if u can do a wound or 2 or make them move only 1 site a turn it&#39;s a sucseful turn.<br />
<br />
Elrond and the hobbits support your party by drawing eaxtra cards. with like 12 or 13 strength bonus cards u will use him to draw them. The hobbits heal frodo and take a hit for the team.<br />
